l my ideas at once! Maybe... Anyhow, just wanted to let you know you can pick up centi war spears very cheap in bazaar, I picked one up for 30pp... They normally go for about 100pp but you just gotta wait for those nice deals.  They're great for training piercing if you don't want to be losing too much damage output, all at the same time :)<br><br>Stats are as follows:<br><br>Centi Warspear Submitted by: Taerun  <br>LORE ITEM MAGIC ITEM  <br>Damage: 20<br>Delay: 30 <br>Ratio: 1.5 Amazing <br>AC: +5 Str: +5 Sta: +5  <br>Weight: 7.0 <br>Weapon Skill: Piercing <br>Classes: Paladin Shadowknight Warrior  <br>Races: All Races  <br>Inventory Slot: Primary Melee<br> Required: Yes <br>Can be stored in Medium and larger containers <br>Last updated: Fri Dec 28 15:52:32 2001 <br> <br><br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sun Aug  4 21:10:58 2002</em></p>&nbsp;<br>Senbik -- Gnomish Shadow Knight of Bertoxxulous.<br>Vindayan -- Dark Elven Shadow Knight of Innoruuk.</td></td></tr>
